INCREDIBLE!!! Red Bull stunt pilot @costadario has broken INSANE (!) World Records this morning as he flew through two tunnels near Istanbul, Turkey✈️ 

- Longest tunnel flown through with an airplane: (1,610m)

- First aeroplane flight through a tunnel

- Longest flight under a solid obstacle 

- First aeroplane flight through two tunnels

- First aeroplane takeoff from a tunnel

The Italian pilot reached an average speed of 245,07kph while flying between 70-160 cm above the asphalt in the second tunnel!👀 

#RedBull #StuntPilot #DarioCosta #GuinessWorldRecord #Istanbul #Turkey
